## Outputs

Per S12 + S13:

```
studies/<slug>/
├── BLUEPRINT.md             # (input)
├── TRANSPOSITION.md         # (input)
├── build-plan.md            # /autoplan-full-compatible plan for /autobuild
├── BUILD-LOG.md             # commit → blueprint section linkage
└── FIDELITY-EVAL.md         # mechanism property status

evals/
└── fidelity/
    ├── <slug>.jsonl         # S13 fidelity contract (one row per property)
    └── <slug>/              # matching test files (/eval-harness consumes)

<target-dir>/
├── ...                      # scaffolded code (STAY skeletons, ADAPT adapters,
                             #  REPLACE stubs, slot interface stubs)
```

